   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#7018509314851307192_64780-h-17.htm.html#FNanchor_57" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">57)</text:span></text:a> Feuerbach, Vogt, Moleschott.</text:p>
